## Development Workflow

### Before Starting Any Task
1. ✅ Confirm feature is in current MVP phase
2. ✅ Check if it can be done without paid services
3. ✅ Plan how to keep app working during development
4. ✅ Identify what tests are needed

### During Development
1. ✅ Use feature branches for complex features
2. ✅ Test after every significant change
3. ✅ Keep backend and frontend in sync
4. ✅ Update API documentation if adding endpoints

### Before Committing
1. ✅ Test full user flow end-to-end
2. ✅ Ensure no console errors
3. ✅ Verify app loads without crashes
4. ✅ Update relevant documentation
5. ✅ Run `npm run dev` successfully

