## Decision Framework

### Should I Implement This Feature?

```
Is it in current MVP phase?
├─ NO → STOP. Document request, wait for explicit approval
└─ YES
   │
   Does it require paid services?
   ├─ YES → Can it use mock/free alternatives?
   │  ├─ NO → STOP. Discuss with user first
   │  └─ YES → Proceed with free alternative
   └─ NO → Proceed
      │
      Will it keep the app working?
      ├─ NO → Use feature flag or branch strategy
      └─ YES → Implement fully, test, commit
```

